{"tid":1265468,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中資壟斷羊毛兼欠款　非洲農民：寧燒掉也不賣予中国人","createTime":"2019-06-29T07:56:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T05:06:12.000Z","uid":184679,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cbc7741abde3222f9f7c61bb3b3d7575b66a4be7","tid":1265468,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T07:56:25.000Z","msg":"非洲小國萊索托的數千名農民周五（28日）往國會示威，抗議政府規定他們把羊毛及優質的馬海毛，售予一間中國中介商。在遊行前一日，政府暫緩協議，讓農民向其他國家售賣產品。<br />\n<br />\n該中介去年與該國簽訂壟斷有關產品購買權的協議，但被指收貨後拖欠貨款。農民舉起標語，批評政府部長逼害他們，又指寧燒掉產品也不賣予中國商人。<br />\n<br />\n執政黨部分成員、反對黨及國王的弟弟均對農民表示支持，逼使政府在示威早一日讓步，暫緩協議3個月。萊索托位於非洲南部，全境被南非所包圍，羊毛及馬海毛過往均是售予南非的中介商，不少農民反對把貨品賣給中國商人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190629/mobile/bkn-20190629001034864-0629_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190629%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190629001034864-0629_00912_001.html&d=FYZ0PdCaIZeH%2BWUkJYSmq05YX6KrfwXAFWAh9WWXcag%3D&h=58f1826e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190629/mobile/bkn-20190629001034864-0629_00912_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://instagram.fist1-2.fna.fbcdn.net/vp/589728d9a64b7fb291f86c0ca3adca5b/5DC2491B/t51.2885-15/sh0.08/e35/s640x640/60324091_123541995510682_9104866676186223538_n.jpg?_nc_ht=instagram.fist1-2.fna.fbcdn.net\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.fist1-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fvp%2F589728d9a64b7fb291f86c0ca3adca5b%2F5DC2491B%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fsh0.08%2Fe35%2Fs640x640%2F60324091_123541995510682_9104866676186223538_n.jpg%3F_nc_ht%3Dinstagram.fist1-2.fna.fbcdn.net&h=8329836a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb69f89590773bddd610af654321bc7ab217aacd","tid":1265468,"uid":158977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T07:57:02.000Z","msg":"nigger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho